content:
Argor was a Human male and a Lesser Prophet of the Dark Side, one of the Emperor's Mages at the time of the Battle of Yavin.
Unlike many higher-ranking Prophets who stayed on Imperial Center and Dromund Kaas, Argor served as a field agent of the Prophets of the Dark Side, foiling Rebel activity in the Outer Rim Territories.
